author: IGN
description:
Take a look at the latest trailer for Destiny: Rising, the upcoming mobile sci-fi RPG shooter game set in the Destiny universe, and meet Gwynn, the Reaper, a wandering executioner who roams the land, delivering Death's judgment unto the guilty. Destiny: Rising is coming to Apple App Store and Google Play Store on August 28, 2025.

#ign #gaming #DestinyRisingGwynn
title: Destiny: Rising - Official Gwynn Character Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Don't miss the Console Launch Overview Trailer for Delta Force, an upcoming free-to-play action first-person shooter developed by Team Jade. The console version offers new maps, new operators, more vehicles, exclusive weapon appearances, and more. Delta Force is launching on PlayStation 5 (PS5) and Xbox Series X|S on August 19.

#ign #gaming #DeltaForce
title: Delta Force - Official Console Launch Overview Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Watch the Lucy Starter Guide Overview Trailer for Guilty Gear Strive, an action fighting game developed by Arc System Works. Get the rundown on how best to use Lucy and unleash a complex offense by applying debuffs with her hacking skills. Lucy is scheduled to be released on August 21, 2025 with the Season Pass 4 of Guilty Gear Strive on PlayStation 4 (PS4), PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch, and PC (Steam).

#ign #GuiltyGearStriveLucy #gaming
title: Guilty Gear Strive - Official Lucy Starter Guide Overview Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Check out the latest trailer for Wuthering Waves, the free-to-play open world action role-playing game developed and published by Kuro Games. Get a look at the latest update version 2.6 - By Sun’s Scourge, By Moon’s Revelation - which will launch on PlayStation 5 (PS5) and PC on August 28, 2025.
